# Pizza ontology fragment — NTriples
# Simplified representative subset for integration testing.
# Namespaces used:
#   pizza: http://example.org/pizza#
#   rdf:   http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#
#   rdfs:  http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#
#   owl:   http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#

# Ontology declaration
<http://example.org/pizza> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .

# Class declarations
<http://example.org/pizza#Food> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#Pizza> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#VegetarianPizza> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#MeatyPizza> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#IceCream> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#Topping> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#VegetableTopping> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://example.org/pizza#MeatTopping> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .

# subClassOf hierarchy
<http://example.org/pizza#Pizza> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://example.org/pizza#Food> .
<http://example.org/pizza#IceCream> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://example.org/pizza#Food> .
<http://example.org/pizza#VegetarianPizza> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://example.org/pizza#Pizza> .
<http://example.org/pizza#MeatyPizza> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://example.org/pizza#Pizza> .
<http://example.org/pizza#VegetableTopping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://example.org/pizza#Topping> .
<http://example.org/pizza#MeatTopping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://example.org/pizza#Topping> .

# Disjointness — VegetarianPizza and MeatyPizza are disjoint
<http://example.org/pizza#VegetarianPizza> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <http://example.org/pizza#MeatyPizza> .
